  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/f9c751931f4b50ce86403fa22b078ef7.poster.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/f9c751931f4b50ce86403fa22b078ef7.webm?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/f9c751931f4b50ce86403fa22b078ef7.mp4?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"O! Holy Knight\" invites you to embark on an exhilarating journey into a medieval fantasy world teeming with peril and adventure. Assume the role of the Holy Knight, tasked with leading a formidable squad of warriors through treacherous landscapes, defeating relentless waves of monstrous foes.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/1f01778a2822346287d95e1bd8380dbe.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=109 /></span><br>Ascend to the helm of tactical mastery as you control the intricate formations of your medieval squad. Direct knights, archers, and mages with precision, orchestrating a dance of blades and magic on the battlefield. Harness the power of strategic formation to exploit enemy weaknesses, creating an unbreakable wall against the relentless waves of monstrous adversaries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/732d3db4316b2b6730532184cbb5ed67.poster.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/732d3db4316b2b6730532184cbb5ed67.webm?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/732d3db4316b2b6730532184cbb5ed67.mp4?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/74540b523753813cbadd9d7c40aca27c.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=109 /></span><br>Celebrate every hard-won victory as your squad gains invaluable experience, unlocking a myriad of skills and abilities. Tailor your unit's prowess, creating powerful synergies that complement your meticulously crafted formations. Evolve your strategy dynamically, ensuring your squad stands resilient against the ever-intensifying challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/a3c91b5819032fb3c45a4a9b869ff61e.poster.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/a3c91b5819032fb3c45a4a9b869ff61e.webm?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/a3c91b5819032fb3c45a4a9b869ff61e.mp4?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/f09d4e878293dcfae766ed2c0d968765.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=109 /></span><br>Immerse yourself in the stunning, high-fidelity world of \"O! Holy Knight\" with captivating cell-shaded visuals. Watch as your medieval warband comes to life in vibrant, toon-rendered detail. Every knight, archer, and mage is meticulously crafted to deliver a visually striking experience, ensuring that every formation and battle unfolds with flair.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/f9c751931f4b50ce86403fa22b078ef7.poster.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/f9c751931f4b50ce86403fa22b078ef7.webm?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/f9c751931f4b50ce86403fa22b078ef7.mp4?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"O! Holy Knight\" invites you to embark on an exhilarating journey into a medieval fantasy world teeming with peril and adventure. Assume the role of the Holy Knight, tasked with leading a formidable squad of warriors through treacherous landscapes, defeating relentless waves of monstrous foes.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/1f01778a2822346287d95e1bd8380dbe.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=109 /></span><br>Ascend to the helm of tactical mastery as you control the intricate formations of your medieval squad. Direct knights, archers, and mages with precision, orchestrating a dance of blades and magic on the battlefield. Harness the power of strategic formation to exploit enemy weaknesses, creating an unbreakable wall against the relentless waves of monstrous adversaries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/732d3db4316b2b6730532184cbb5ed67.poster.avif?t=1707232368\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682370/extras/732d3db4316b2b6730532184cbb5ed67.webm?t=1707232368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=v